          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1683717161457-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>onion petals</strong> and <strong>halved tomatoes</strong> to one side of a<strong> baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Sprinkle over 3/4<strong> </strong>of the <strong>ras el hanout</strong> (save the rest for later!) with a grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span>in the oven for 15 min or until slightly charred – this is your <strong>roast veg</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
