    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Roll the <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in quarters</p><p>Combine the <strong>natural</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong> and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>harissa paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>in a small bowl with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>honey </strong>and the juice of 1/4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1/2]</span> <strong>lemon </strong>– this is your<strong> yoghurt & harissa dressing</strong></p>",
